snippet.title: On The Fly
snippet.description:
On The Fly is a combination Endless Runner & Dating Sim made for Ludum Dare 41. Two birds, their love forbidden by their families, escape down a river on a rusty old kettle. They’ll eat flies to stay full, dodge floating debris, and share some quiet moments together.

Art: Rebecca Kremer - @FlightyFelon on Twitter
Dev: Joshua Hurd - @qkjosh on Twitter
